              "description": {
                "paragraph": [
                  "BioTuf Compostable Trash Bags are some of the strongest compostable trash bags available. These bags meet the ASTM D6400 standards and are certified by the Biodegradable Products Institute guaranteeing these trash bags will compost along with other organic materials. BioTuf Compostable Trash Bags have performance similar to regular plastic trash bags. These compostable trash bags have a star-sealed bottom which is nearly leakproof and allows transportation of refuse without concern of causing a mess. BioTuf Compostable Trash Bags come in coreless rolls for ease of use and also have a convenient dual dispensing box."
                ],
                "descriptionLineSize": 2,
                "bullets": [
                  "60-64 Gallon Trash Bags, 47x60",
